    Manages the value for a single key in a HeatMapCache.
    HeatMapCacheEntry.Status
    Status of an entry in the cache: NOT_LOADED - No value is available and none is in the process of loading LOADING - No value is currently available, but it is in the process of loading LOADED - Value is loaded and available

    Gives access to HeatMapCache instances, by type.
